body:
Hello,

To provide some insight on what we're currenlty planning inside the event team, and for future events, the Officials have decided to host a Q&A session on TeamSpeak. Anyone can ask questions and we will answer them to the best of our ability (As long as we don't release classified information).

There will be two sessions, an Australian session, hosted by Mango and Jozz, and a American/European session hosted by myself.

Time for the Australian session it 7pm AEST.

The EU session will be held at 2pm EDT/EST.

The event will be held the 15th of August.

Any question about the event can be asked below.

Regards,
The Officials.
